Privacy Policy

Your privacy is important to us. This privacy policy explains how we handle information in our checkers game.

1. information Collection
We do not collect, store, or share any personally identifiable information from our users. Our game is designed to operate without the need for personal data.

2. In-App Purchases
Our game offers in-app purchases managed by Google Play. During a purchase, Google Play may collect and process certain personal information in accordance with its own privacy policy. We do not have access to this information and do not store it.

3. Advertisements and Third-Party Services
Our game may display advertisements provided by third parties or include third-party services. These parties may collect anonymous information to provide tailored advertisements or services. We recommend reviewing the privacy policies of the advertising providers for more information.

4. Security
While we do not collect any personal data, we are committed to protecting any information you may share with us, such as through customer support communications.

5. Changes to the Privacy Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page.

6. Contact
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this privacy policy, please contact us at [heybasup@gmail.com].
